      "args": {
        "text": "COLOR ONLY: BANK 1 PLACEMENT\nAll composed pair tiles now live in\nVRAM tile data bank 1, selected per\nmap cell by attribute bit 3, so the\nreserved indices 128-191 no longer\ncompete with bank 0 scene tiles.\nPress A",
