      "args": {
        "text": "!S3!ALTERNATE PLACEMENT\nPair tiles now alternate between bank\n0 and bank 1, so the same 64-tile\nrange caches twice as many pairs.\nWatch both VRAM banks fill in a\ndebugger while this types out.\nPress A",
